<page path="/signup">
    <header></header>
    <form action="/api/auth/signup">
        <title>회원가입 및 거래처 등록</title>
        <error-message />
        
        <section>
            <subtitle>계정 정보</subtitle>
            <input type="email" label="이메일" required />
            <input type="password" label="비밀번호" required />
            <input type="password" label="비밀번호 확인" required />
            <input type="text" label="담당자명" required />
            <input type="tel" label="연락처" required />
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <subtitle>거래처 정보</subtitle>
            <input type="text" label="업체명" required />
            <select label="업체 유형" required>
                <option value="wholesale">도매업체</option>
                <option value="retail">소매업체</option>
            </select>
            <input type="text" label="사업자등록번호" required />
            <input type="text" label="업체 주소" required />
            <textarea label="업체 소개" />
        </section>
        
        <notice>
            회원가입 신청 후 관리자 승인이 필요합니다.
        </notice>
        
        <button type="submit">가입 신청</button>
    </form>
    <text>
    이미 계정이 있으신가요? <link href="/login">로그인</link>
    </text>
    <footer></footer>
</page>